Package: ggphylogeo
Type: Package
Title: ggplot2 Tools for Continuous Phylogeography
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Joon", "Klaps", email = "joon.klaps@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Visualization tools for BEAST continuous phylogeographic
    analyses using ggplot2. Provides functions to build and plot branch
    segments, HPD polygons, and nodes from treedata objects. Includes
    an interactive Shiny application for exploring phylogeographic data.
